  "headline": "Track and Field Events",
  "description": "Track and field (athletics) comprises running, jumping, and throwing events dating to Ancient Olympics. Sprint events (100m-400m) emphasize explosive power; distance events require aerobic endurance. Field events: long jump, high jump, pole vault, shot put, discus, javelin, hammer. Decathlon/heptathlon tests all-around athleticism.",
